---
import aboutus from "../../public/Images/aboutus.png";
---

<section class="my-[120px]">
    <div
        class="container-xl mx-auto flex w-full flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-[34px]"
    >
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-[40px] font-bold mb-4">About Us</h2>
            <p class="text-[18px] mb-4 font-inter">
                Founded In 2015, BI Insights Emerged From A Simple Yet Powerful
                Vision: To Democratize Data-Driven Decision Making For
                Businesses Of All Sizes. Our Founders, Seasoned Data
                Professionals From Fortune 500 Companies, Recognized That Many
                Organizations Were Sitting On Goldmines Of Data But Lacked The
                Expertise To Extract Meaningful Insights.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[18px] mb-4 font-inter">
                What Started As A Small Consulting Firm Has Grown Into A Trusted
                Partner For Over 200 Companies Worldwide. We've Helped
                Organizations Across Healthcare, Finance, Retail, And Technology
                Sectors Transform Their Data Into Competitive Advantages.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[18px] mb-4 font-inter">
                Today, We Continue To Innovate At The Intersection Of Business
                Strategy And Cutting-Edge Analytics, Helping Our Clients
                Navigate The Complexities Of Modern Data Landscapes.
            </p>
            <button
                class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-white"
                style="background-color: #FF9929;"
            >
                Work With Us
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img
                src={aboutus.src}
                alt="Data analytics dashboard"
                class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-lg"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
